OL,4,CBrazil 'needs $10bn to reach zero
OL,5,Cemissions' says minister
OL,6, Brazil's environment minister says the
OL,7, country needs $10bn (#7.2bn) a year in
OL,8, foreign aid in order to reach zero
OL,9, emissions by 2050.
OL,11,FThe move would mean that Brazil could
OL,12,Fachieve the symbolic figure 10 years
OL,13,Fearlier than currently planned.
OL,15,FIt comes ahead of US President Joe
OL,16,FBiden's climate summit next week.
OL,18,FBrazil's environmental policies have
OL,19,Fbrought international condemnation
OL,20,Fsince President Jair Bolsonaro took
OL,21,Foffice two years ago.
